<br>
The problem is you are misunderstanding the Beastlord class.  &quot;Beastlord&quot; is a bit of a misnomer, but basically what they are doing is calling in a spirit Warder from the spirit-realm.  This is why after a certain amount of time a Warder &quot;poofs&quot;, because they can no longer maintain their presence on the material world.<br>
<br>
Beastlords are in essence a mix between Monks and Shaman (who also derive their power from the spirit-realm)...<br>
<br>
Notice how neither of those classes track.<br>
<br>
I said it once, I'll say it again ... Iksar do not <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  need</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> tracking, you guys just <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  want</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> it.<br>
